snippet.title: Donkey Kong Country 2: Diddy Kong's Quest Trailer 1995
snippet.description:
Donkey Kong Country 2: Diddy Kong's Quest Trailer 1995

Official Content From Nintendo Of America

The mighty Donkey Kong has been kidnapped by the evil King K. Rool. His only hope is to be rescued by his monkey friend, Diddy, and his girlfriend, Dixie. Better get moving!
Platforms: Super Nintendo
